parameters:
\n<Eury>If there's anything you'd like to ask of a modified girl,
please feel free!
\n<Master>Would you like to work at my tavern?

\n<Master>I'm sure having a new model girl around would definitely
increase our customers! Please!

\n<Eury>(Hehe♪ Using the novelty of a new model modified girl to
increase the number of visitors, huh?)

\n<Eury>(It's a bit different from my usual work as a modified girl,
but if my popularity can help liven up the town even a
little, that would be great♪)
\n<Master>Oh, that's great to hear! Then I'm counting on you.

\n<Master>I know you're busy, Eury-chan, so just come and work
whenever you can. It's all good.

\n<Eury>(Working at the tavern... I often get called clumsy by Dr.
Marion, but I wonder if I'll be okay?)

\n<Eury>(...No! I'm not clumsy! Because I am a modified girl after
all!)

\n<Master>It's simple, just carry the ordered items to the customers
and that's good.

\n<Master>(A state-of-the-art sexaroid working in the shop. This will
definitely boost our customer attraction...!)

\n<Eury>(This is also for the sake of Tengatsu Street! I have to
work hard for the reconstruction!)
\n<Master>Then, please take this to that table over there.
\n<Customer 1>Oh, are you perhaps the new model?!
\n<Customer 2>A new model working at a tavern...

\n<Eury>That's right~! It's not my main job, but it's all for
everyone's sake!

\n<Customer 1>(Amazing, the more I look, the more she seems like a regular
human...!)

\n<Customer 2>It's impressive that you can handle tasks other than your
main job so well.

\n<Customer 2>(Normal sexaroids can't do anything properly besides sex,
after all.)
\n<Customer 1>Come on, it's fine, it's fine, since...
\n<Customer 2>No way, no way! I won't allow any cheating!
\n<Eury>Um, that's troubling, so could you not...

\n<Eury>(To think he'd sexually harass someone upon meeting them,
what kind of nerve is that?!)

\n<Eury>(...Maybe people who only deal with sexaroids are just
sexually frustrated?)
\n<Eury>Oh, no, please don't worry about it.
\n<Master>Next, please serve that table over there.
\n<Eury>(I want to punch him...! But I can't lay a hand on him...)

\n<Customer 3>Don't be like that~! The new model's boobs belong to
everyone, right~!
\n<Customer 3>Is this where the nipple is? Look, I'm rubbing it.

\n<Master>I'm sorry, Eury-chan. We do get troublesome customers from
time to time.

\n<Master>(Even if she's a sexaroid, being messed with in public is
bad for the shop's image.)
\n<Master>You've worked hard today. You can rest now; it's okay.
\n<Master>Yes, good job. Here, this is for your hard work today.
\n<Master>This Glow Core is a valuable substance, you know.

\n<Master>I have no idea what it's used for... but since Marion-san
wanted it, I'll give it to you.
\n<Eury>(With this, I can become stronger as a modified girl!)

\n<Master>(Since Marion-san is the developer of sexaroids, if I give
it to this girl, it'll reach her.)
